playstore_details.title: Radiology Assistant
playstore_details.description:
This is the Radiology Assistant for Android. An invaluable imaging reference with over 90 articles written by expert radiologists!

FEATURES
• Intuitive layout and search function makes it easy to find the article you're looking for! 
• Text search function to look for specific words in an article.
• Enlarging images enables pinch-zoom. This also shows the underlying high-res version 
  in many of the images.
• Scroll functionality in image stacks.
• Frequently updated content.
